# The repository-root .gitignore ignores everything ('*') and then whitelists
# only a few source extensions (*.cpp, *.h, *.txt, *.md, *.ttf, *.wav, ...).
# That silently drops this project's .ogg sound effects. Re-include the assets
# a fresh clone needs so the game actually loads them.

!.gitignore
!*.md
!*.ogg
!*.ttf

# Build artifacts (sudoku_gui, sudoku) and object files have no whitelisted
# extension, so the root '*' already ignores them. Runtime save state is a
# .txt (whitelisted), so ignore it explicitly:
savegame.txt

# Local tooling / editor state
.claude/
